# Local env files at any depth — dev-only overrides (e.g. apps/web/.env.local
# with VITE_SYNC_URL=:3001) must never leak into an image: Vite inlines VITE_*
# at build time, which would bake the wrong API/socket URL into the bundle.
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example
!**/.env.example
